</style></div></div><div class="sc-item is-memories"><div class="sc-heading is-memories-01"><div class="max-width-col-08"><h1 class="heading-style-160px">More where that came from?</h1></div><a href="/projects" class="button w-inline-block"><div class="button-content"><div class="button-text"><div>See all projects</div></div><div class="button-spacing"></div><div class="button-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" class="icon-24"><path d="M5.17773 5.17767L30.1777 5.17767M30.1777 5.17767V30.1777M30.1777 5.17767L5.17773 30.1777" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="square"></path></svg></div></div><div class="button-divider"></div></a><link rel="prefetch" href="/projects"></div><div class="sc-heading is-memories-02"><h1 class="heading-style-160px">Memories<br>that last</h1></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><div nav-scrub="" class="sticky-sections"><div class="sticky-sections_content"><section class="section_showcase"><div class="showcase"><div class="showcase_content"><div class="aspect-ratio-100vh"><div class="image-parallax"><div class="image-parallax_image"><img src="images/679a47babfce33f3228df8d0_MCOADBOYS_CINESTILL%20%2834%29.webp" loading="eager" alt="" sizes="(max-width: 2800px) 100vw, 2800px" srcset="images/679a47babfce33f3228df8d0_MCOADBOYS_CINESTILL%20%2834%29-p-500.webp 500w, images/679a47babfce33f3228df8d0_MCOADBOYS_CINESTILL%20%2834%29-p-800.webp 800w, images/679a47babfce33f3228df8d0_MCOADBOYS_CINESTILL%20%2834%29-p-1080.webp 1080w, images/679a47babfce33f3228df8d0_MCOADBOYS_CINESTILL%20%2834%29-p-1600.webp 1600w, images/679a47babfce33f3228df8d0_MCOADBOYS_CINESTILL%20%2834%29-p-2000.webp 2000w, images/679a47babfce33f3228df8d0_MCOADBOYS_CINESTILL%20%2834%29-p-2600.webp 2600w, images/679a47babfce33f3228df8d0_MCOADBOYS_CINESTILL%20%2834%29.webp 2800w" class="image"></div><div class="image-parallax_trigger is-section-100vh"></div></div></div></div></div></section></div><div navbar-scrub="" clas